title: Week 7 preview & Bears vs Packers recap
itunes:title: Week 7 preview & Bears vs Packers recap
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Chris Wesseling & Colleen Wolfe – go game-by-game recapping each week 7 matchup, including an update from Gregg Rosenthal who is holding down the fort in London. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night game between the Chicago Bears and the Green Bay Packers.
